Résumé du projet

Informations sur le projet

Champ Valeur
Nom mybatis
Description The MyBatis data mapper framework makes it easier to use a relational database with object-oriented applications. MyBatis couples objects with stored procedures or SQL statements using a XML descriptor or annotations. Simplicity is the biggest advantage of the MyBatis data mapper over object relational mapping tools.
Page d'accueil http://www.mybatis.org/core/
